The paper is about information retrieval (IR) evaluation, which is a subfield of information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also discusses topic selection methods, which are relevant to natural language processing (NLP) and computational linguistics (cs.CL) as well as artificial intelligence (AI) and machine learning (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the cost-effectiveness of different evaluation methods, which is relevant to machine learning (cs.LG) and cybernetics (cs.CY).
